data.description: Experience the epitome of comfort and style in this immaculate residence! Presenting the exquisite Holiday Builder's most desirable split bedroom Dogwood floor plan. This move-in-ready home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a seamlessly integrated open kitchen-dining room area that effortlessly flows into a spacious great room. Revel in the luxury of a 2021 built home. Indulge in the lifestyle you've always dreamed of with access to a community pool and gym, providing the perfect setting for relaxation and entertainment. The prime location adds to the allure, offering convenience just minutes away from local shopping and dining establishments. Embrace the coastal charm as you find yourself in close proximity to the breathtaking beaches of Walton County, making every day a vacation.
